*sprockets-3.2.0 (22 Jun 2015)

  22 Jun 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +sprockets-3.2.0.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  07 Jun 2015; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  Add github to remote-id in metadata.xml

*sprockets-2.12.3-r1 (02 Jun 2015)

  02 Jun 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +sprockets-2.12.3-r1.ebuild,
  sprockets-3.1.0.ebuild:
  Fix slot collision for binstub, bug 550866.

*sprockets-3.1.0 (14 May 2015)

  14 May 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> sprockets-2.12.3.ebuild,
  +sprockets-3.1.0.ebuild:
  Version bump. Add missing uglifier test dependency.

  11 Apr 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -sprockets-2.1.4.ebuild:
  Remove masked ruby19-only packages.

  17 Nov 2014; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> sprockets-2.11.3.ebuild:
  Don't install the bin script to avoid a file collision with later slots.

*sprockets-2.11.3 (17 Nov 2014)

  17 Nov 2014; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +sprockets-2.11.3.ebuild:
  Add a 2.11 version of sprockets because it turns out 2.12 is not compatible
  with 2.11.

  07 Nov 2014; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -sprockets-2.1.3.ebuild,
  -sprockets-2.2.2-r1.ebuild, -sprockets-2.11.0.ebuild,
  -sprockets-2.12.2.ebuild:
  Remove vulnerable versions.

