*sprockets-2.12.2 (02 Oct 2014)

  02 Oct 2014; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +sprockets-2.12.2.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  04 Sep 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> sprockets-2.2.2-r1.ebuild:
  Add ruby21 target. Simplify deps.

  16 Aug 2014; Anthony G. Basile <blueness@gentoo.org> sprockets-2.1.3.ebuild,
  sprockets-2.11.0.ebuild, sprockets-2.2.2-r1.ebuild:
  Keyword on ~ppc and ~ppc64, request by mrueg

  05 Aug 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> sprockets-2.1.3.ebuild,
  sprockets-2.11.0.ebuild, sprockets-2.2.2-r1.ebuild:
  Remove trailing '.' from DESCRIPTION.

  04 May 2014; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> sprockets-2.2.2-r1.ebuild:
  Add ruby20 target.

  20 Apr 2014; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> sprockets-2.11.0.ebuild:
  Add ruby21. Update execjs dependency. Fix tests broken by our use of ln to
  populate the ruby target directories.

  20 Apr 2014; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> -sprockets-2.2.2.ebuild,
  -sprockets-2.10.0.ebuild, -sprockets-2.10.1.ebuild:
